data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER ** Bring Offers **Very spacious floor plan that is open and also has a Bonus room, which could be a great office and or entertainment room, or game area. Home is in a great location centrally located in Callaway and only 15 Min to Tyndall base, and within 5 Min for shopping and points of interest. New roof back in 2019, New water heater, LVT flooring in Living area with carpets in bedrooms. Owner will be replacing the carpets in the bedrooms.
